nodes.text: Kral'to was a location in the Outer Rim Territories. The elders of Kral'to told the tale of an ancient traveler who could cure diseases.

In 5 ABY, the RA-7 protocol droid FR-D 8T-KA mentioned the elders of Kral'to during a conversation with the cyborg Beilert Valance. The protocol droid described them as one of the various Outer Rim cultures that had legends of organics being restored.
